{"_id":"DG9EWJXKW424PI5x","name":"Persistent Dread","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>Your Object of Enmity is frightened, it is the end of their turn, and the value of their frightened condition will drop.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You threaten a foe with divine wrath if they find their resolve. You command your foe to stay frightened and not drop the value of their frightened condition. The foe must choose one of the following options.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Object of Enmity's value of their frightened condition does not drop.</li>\n<li>Your Object of Enmity refuses, and you deal 3d8 damage to it. This damage increases to 4d8 at 12th level, 5d8 at 16th level, and 6d8 at 19th level. The damage type matches your Divine Fury damage type.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Avenger - The Divine Striker by Fanatic66"},"traits":{"value":["hb_avenger","emotion","fear","mental"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-03T19:56:13.642-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FK7E3AY7JEA3lsGP","name":"Shielding Shadows","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirement </strong>You are in dim light.<br /><strong>Trigger </strong>Your Object of Enmity makes a Strike against you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You call upon the shadows to protect you. You become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} until the start of your next turn.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Avenger - The Divine Striker by Fanatic66"},"traits":{"value":["hb_avenger","shadow"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-03T19:55:02.824-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TvxLWSicGK9NSZSH","name":"Pursue Emnity","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>Your Object of Enmity attempts to move away from you using an action that has the move trait while adjacent to you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You follow your foe. Stride up to your speed in tandem with your Object of Enmity, remaining adjacent to the foe throughout its movement until it stops moving or you run out of movement. If you end your movement within reach of your Object of Enmity, you can Strike at the creature.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Avenger - The Divine Striker by Fanatic66"},"traits":{"value":["hb_avenger","move"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-03T19:53:56.179-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XeV3ZTW8YMi77qP3","name":"Find Weakness","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>You or an ally within 15 feet succeed on a melee Strike against you Object of Emnity, and you have successfully identified you Object of Emnity with Recall Knowledge during this round.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Using your past insight on a foe, you discern how to make an attack truly hurt. The attack deals an additional 2d6 precision damage. If are legendary in the skill that you used to identify your Object of Enmity with Recall Knowledge, then the additional damage increases to 3d6.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Avenger - The Divine Striker by Fanatic66"},"traits":{"value":["hb_avenger"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-03T19:50:59.590-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"urSZx8bDDja6we8n","name":"Opportune Strike","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally succeeds at a melee Strike against your Object of Enmity and you are adjacent to your Object of Enmity.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You follow up with your ally's attack. Make a melee Strike with a &ndash;2 penalty against your Object of Enmity.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Avenger - The Divine Striker by Fanatic66"},"traits":{"value":["hb_avenger"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-03T19:57:41.377-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3},"flags":{}}
